EASTERN CARIBBEAN SEA.
DOMINICA-SOUTHWEST COAST.
SIX METER F/V SUCK A BONE, YELLOW AND WHITE HULL,
TWO PERSONS ON BOARD, OVERDUE PORT ROSEUA (15-18N 061-23W)
AND RETURN. VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED TO KEEP
A SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF POSSIBLE. REPORTS TO
MRCC FORT DE FRANCE, TELEX: 42912008,
PHONE: 5965 9670 9292, FAX: 5965 9663 2450.
